Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.38,0:12:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hececec&}原来只是僵尸而已！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.76,0:12:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,老师心情真不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.68,0:12:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,能看出来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.52,0:12:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.18,0:12:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,都写在脸上了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.35,0:12:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,赶上发薪日
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.72,0:12:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我想去看明天上映的这部电影
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.32,0:12:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我也很期待这部呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.72,0:12:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.11,0:12:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,那明天一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.56,0:12:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.60,0:12:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,那就说定了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.03,0:12:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,之后再联系
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.54,0:13:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,1000)\be3\3c&HAC7613&\4c&HFFFFFF&\pos(650,396)}不经意之随意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.13,0:12:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,自己都没注意到今天有点奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.73,0:13:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,居然想都没想就邀请他了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.11,0:13:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,这完全就是所谓的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.04,0:13:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,约会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.93,0:13:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\fs25}对老师的约会做何感想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.93,0:13:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\fs23}想吃炒面面包
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.93,0:13:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\fs25}加油
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.93,0:13:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\fs25}随便
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.93,0:13:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\fs25}放弃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.93,0:13:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\fs25}无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.93,0:13:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\fs25}电器街员工调查
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.04,0:13:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.32,0:13:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,是我该说对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.76,0:13:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.52,0:13:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,听话 别乱动
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.70,0:13:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,粘上爆米花了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.48,0:13:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你的眼睛跟爆米花可不搭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.14,0:13:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,这是第一次两人单独出去玩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.11,0:13:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.64,0:13:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,总之先得准备一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.35,0:13:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,这种打扮可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.47,0:13:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,要穿得更可爱些
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.58,0:13:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,要换成隐形眼镜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.42,0:13:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,要涂唇彩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.38,0:13:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,海雄 让你久等了
